# Keep the Docker build context small and free of local/secret cruft. The
# relay image needs the workspace sources + root manifests + lockfile only.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.svelte-kit
**/build
.git
.github
.claude
.emdash
.changeset
**/*.log
**/coverage
**/.turbo
# never ship local env files into an image layer
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
deploy/relay/.env
# docs/tests-only heavy dirs are fine to include (tsx runs from source), but
# these are pure noise for a server image:
**/.DS_Store
scratchpad
